HENRY-GRIFFITTS, INC., Plaintiff-Appellant, v. ACUSHNET COMPANY (doing business as Titleist Golf), Defendant, and Roger Cleveland Golf Company, Inc., Defendant-Appellee, and Taylor Made Golf Company, Defendant-Appellee. No. 06-1278. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. Nov. 7, 2006.

Before LOURIE, RADER, and SCHALL, Circuit Judges.

*885 JUDGMENT

PER CURIAM.

This CAUSE having been heard and considered, it is ORDERED and ADJUDGED:

AFFIRMED. See Fed. Cir. R. 36.
